<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Projects - Skills Table</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family:'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; margin:0; background:#f7f8fb; color:#111; }
    header { background:#0f172a; color:#fff; padding:20px 16px; }
    nav a { color:#dbeafe; margin-right:14px; text-decoration:none; font-weight:600; }
    nav a:hover { color:#fff; }
    .container { max-width:960px; margin:auto; padding:24px; }
    table { width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; background:#fff; border:1px solid #cbd5e1; box-shadow:0 6px 14px rgba(15,23,42,.12); }
    th, td { padding:12px 14px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; text-align:left; }
    th { background:#e0e7ff; color:#1e3a8a; font-weight:700; }
    td:nth-child(2) { font-weight:600; color:#1f2937; }
    tr:nth-child(even) { background:#f8fafc; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <nav>
      <a href="index.html2">Home</a>
      <a href="project.ht">Projects</a>
      <a href="contact.ht">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Skills Table</h1>
    <p>Neeche quality-focused technology, proficiency aur experience dikhayi gayi hai.</p>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Technology</th>
          <th>Proficiency</th>
          <th>Experience</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>HTML</td><td>Advanced</td><td>4+ saal</td></tr>
        <tr><td>CSS / SCSS</td><td>Advanced</td><td>4+ saal</td></tr>
        <tr><td>JavaScript</td><td>Advanced</td><td>3+ saal</td></tr>
        <tr><td>React</td><td>Intermediate</td><td>2 saal</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Node.js</td><td>Intermediate</td><td>1.5 saal</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Git</td><td>Advanced</td><td>4+ saal</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
